<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Workout Home</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body.home-page {
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.08), transparent 28%),
                radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.10), transparent 22%),
                linear-gradient(180deg, #f5f7fb 0%, #edf2f7 100%);
            color: #10233b;
        }

        .app-topbar,
        .home-topbar {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0f172a 0%, #172235 100%) !important;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.18);
            box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18);
        }

        .app-topbar .navbar-brand,
        .home-topbar .navbar-brand {
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            color: #f8fafc;
        }

        .app-topbar .nav-link {
            color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.82);
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.35rem 0.25rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .app-topbar .nav-link:hover,
        .app-topbar .nav-link.active {
            color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom-color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8);
        }

        .app-topbar-profile {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 2.3rem;
            height: 2.3rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
            color: #e2e8f0;
            transition: background 140ms ease, border-color 140ms ease, color 140ms ease;
        }

        .app-topbar-profile:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            border-color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.36);
        }

        .app-topbar-profile__icon {
            width: 1rem;
            height: 1rem;
        }

        .app-topbar .btn {
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding-inline: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.28);
        }

        .app-topbar .btn-outline-danger {
            color: #fecaca;
            border-color: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.32);
            background: rgba(127, 29, 29, 0.18);
        }

        .app-topbar .btn-outline-danger:hover {
            color: #fff1f2;
            background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.28);
            border-color: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.45);
        }

        .home-topbar .navbar-brand {
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            color: #f8fafc;
        }

        .home-topbar .btn {
            border-radius: 999px !important;
            padding-inline: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-width: 1px;
        }

        .home-topbar .btn-outline-light {
            color: #e2e8f0;
            border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        }

        .home-topbar .btn-outline-light:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            border-color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.36);
        }

        .home-topbar .btn-light {
            color: #e2e8f0;
            border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        }

        .home-topbar .btn-light:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            border-color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.36);
        }

        .home-auth-card__body .btn {
            border-radius: 999px !important;
        }

        .home-shell {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .home-hero {
            display: flex;
            align-items: end;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.25);
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            background:
                linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.94), rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.92)),
                linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.02), rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.04));
            box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .home-kicker {
            margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.18em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #0f766e;
        }

        .home-title {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 2.8vw, 3rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            line-height: 0.95;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .home-subtitle {
            margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
            max-width: 44rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #475569;
        }

        .home-chip-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .home-chip {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.45rem;
            padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.28);
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
            font-size: 0.83rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e293b;
        }

        .home-chip-label {
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .home-tile-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1.2rem;
        }

        .home-tile {
            display: block;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.22);
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            background:
                linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96), rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.94));
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.07);
            padding: 1.35rem 1.4rem 1.45rem;
            transition: transform 140ms ease, box-shadow 140ms ease, border-color 140ms ease;
        }

        .home-tile:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            border-color: rgba(147, 197, 253, 0.72);
            box-shadow: 0 22px 44px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.10);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .home-tile__eyebrow {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .home-tile__title {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .home-tile__copy {
            margin: 0.65rem 0 0;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            color: #475569;
            line-height: 1.55;
        }

        .home-tile__cta {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.84rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2563eb;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }

        .home-auth-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.15fr) minmax(320px, 0.85fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
            align-items: stretch;
        }

        .home-auth-panel,
        .home-auth-card {
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.22);
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            background:
                linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96), rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.94));
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        }

        .home-auth-panel {
            padding: 1.5rem 1.6rem;
        }

        .home-auth-features {
            display: grid;
            gap: 0.95rem;
            margin-top: 1.3rem;
        }

        .home-auth-feature {
            padding: 1rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 1.1rem;
            background: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.92);
            border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.92);
        }

        .home-auth-feature__title {
            margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
            font-size: 0.96rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .home-auth-feature__copy {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        .home-auth-card {
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .home-auth-card__header {
            padding: 1.1rem 1.35rem 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.85);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.92), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88));
        }

        .home-auth-card__title {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .home-auth-card__body {
            padding: 1.35rem;
        }

        .home-auth-card__body .btn {
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .app-footer {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
        }

        .app-footer a {
            color: #475569;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .app-footer a:hover {
            color: #0f172a;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        @media (max-width: 991.98px) {
            .home-hero {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .home-chip-group {
                justify-content: flex-start;
            }

            .home-tile-grid,
            .home-auth-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="home-page">
    <% if (isAuthenticated) { %>
        <%- include("partials/app-topbar", {
            title: "Home",
            currentPage: "home",
            userInfo,
            showDashboardNewLink: true
        }) %>

        <div class="container-fluid px-3 px-xl-4 py-4">
            <div class="home-shell">
                <section class="home-hero">
                    <div>
                        <p class="home-kicker">App Home</p>
                        <h1 class="home-title">Workout Console</h1>
                        <p class="home-subtitle">
                            Wähle deinen Einstieg in Analyse, Segmente und Upload. Diese Startseite ist bewusst
                            ein Navigations-Hub und nicht die tiefe Analyseansicht selbst.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="home-chip-group">
                        <span class="home-chip">
                            <span class="home-chip-label">User</span>
                            <span><%= userInfo.display_name || userInfo.email || userInfo.username %></span>
                        </span>
                        <span class="home-chip">
                            <span class="home-chip-label">Mode</span>
                            <span>Workspace Hub</span>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="home-tile-grid">
                    <a class="home-tile" href="/dashboard-new">
                        <span class="home-tile__eyebrow">Workout Library</span>
                        <h2 class="home-tile__title">Workouts</h2>
                        <p class="home-tile__copy">
                            Neue edle Workout-Library mit direktem Zugriff auf Chart und Karte.
                        </p>
                        <span class="home-tile__cta">Zur Analyseansicht</span>
                    </a>

                    <a class="home-tile" href="/segments">
                        <span class="home-tile__eyebrow">Map-first Design</span>
                        <h2 class="home-tile__title">Segments</h2>
                        <p class="home-tile__copy">
                            Segmente definieren, vergleichen, Höhenprofile prüfen und Best-Efforts analysieren.
                        </p>
                        <span class="home-tile__cta">Zur Segmentansicht</span>
                    </a>

                    <a class="home-tile" href="/analytics">
                        <span class="home-tile__eyebrow">Training Trends</span>
                        <h2 class="home-tile__title">Analytics</h2>
                        <p class="home-tile__copy">
                            CTL, ATL, FTP und CP-Verläufe in einer dedizierten Trend-Analyse.
                        </p>
                        <span class="home-tile__cta">Zur Analytics-Seite</span>
                    </a>

                    <a class="home-tile" href="/files/uploadUI">
                        <span class="home-tile__eyebrow">Import Runner</span>
                        <h2 class="home-tile__title">Upload</h2>
                        <p class="home-tile__copy">
                            FIT- und ZIP-Dateien hochladen und die Verarbeitung in der Upload-Ansicht verfolgen.
                        </p>
                        <span class="home-tile__cta">Zum Upload</span>
                    </a>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include("partials/app-footer") %>
    <% } else { %>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-dark home-topbar">
            <div class="container-fluid px-3 px-xl-4">
                <span class="navbar-brand">Workout Dashboard</span>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm" href="/login">Login</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-light btn-sm" href="/signup">Sign up</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <div class="container py-4 py-lg-5">
            <div class="home-shell">
                <section class="home-hero">
                    <div>
                        <p class="home-kicker">Welcome</p>
                        <h1 class="home-title">Training Analysis Workspace</h1>
                        <p class="home-subtitle">
                            Lade Workouts hoch, analysiere Leistung und Segmente und bewege dich zwischen
                            Karte, Verlauf und Trainingsdaten in einer konsistenten Oberfläche.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="home-chip-group">
                        <span class="home-chip">
                            <span class="home-chip-label">Focus</span>
                            <span>Analyse · Segmente · Upload</span>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="home-auth-grid">
                    <div class="home-auth-panel">
                        <p class="home-kicker">Platform</p>
                        <h2 class="home-title" style="font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 2.2vw, 2.3rem);">Ein echter Einstieg statt Direkt-Redirect</h2>
                        <p class="home-subtitle" style="max-width:none;">
                            Wenn du noch nicht angemeldet bist, kommst du jetzt auf eine kleine Startseite statt
                            sofort auf eine tiefe Analyseansicht. Von hier aus kannst du dich anmelden oder ein
                            Konto anlegen.
                        </p>

                        <div class="home-auth-features">
                            <div class="home-auth-feature">
                                <h3 class="home-auth-feature__title">Workout Upload</h3>
                                <p class="home-auth-feature__copy">FIT- und ZIP-Dateien importieren und die Verarbeitung verfolgen.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="home-auth-feature">
                                <h3 class="home-auth-feature__title">Segment Analysis</h3>
                                <p class="home-auth-feature__copy">Kartenbasierte Segmentdefinition, Höhenprofile und Best-Efforts.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="home-auth-feature">
                                <h3 class="home-auth-feature__title">Analytics</h3>
                                <p class="home-auth-feature__copy">FTP-, CP- und Load-Trends in einer separaten Analyseansicht.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="home-auth-card">
                        <div class="home-auth-card__header">
                            <h2 class="home-auth-card__title">Weiter zur App</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="home-auth-card__body">
                            <div class="d-grid gap-3">
                                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/login">Login</a>
                                <a class="btn btn-outline-primary" href="/signup">Create account</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include("partials/app-footer") %>
    <% } %>
</body>

</html>
